snippet.title: Best VGM 2410 - Treasure Hunter G - Surrounded by Forest
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 597 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gY9jq9-1LTk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Treasure Hunter G (1996)
Surrounded by Forest
John Pee (Mitsuhito Tanaka)
